snippet.title: Scarlet Nexus - Gamescom 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
The OSF members are showing off their moves in the new #SCARLETNEXUS trailer from #Gamescom2020! Tell us in the comments which power caught your attention!

Enter a brain punk future & unleash the power of the mind. SCARLET NEXUS will arrive to #XboxSeriesX, XboxOne, PS4, PS5, and PC. http://bandainam.co/ScarletNexus

Follow us on:
